content: "8 ton Orca jumping 15ft out of the water...",pic.twitter.com/auHUFBfNDQ

They are the kings of the ocean, so smart & powerful! Don't let SeaWorld fool you, nothing beats a wild orca, not even great whites. Maybe prehistoric Megalodon, if Jason Statham doesn't kill him first...
When you think about it...when an animal that size, weighing as much as it does, jumps 15ft from a non-solid surface such as water, that is NATURAL, BEAUTIFUL RAW POWER!  MAGNIFICENT!!
Wow ,  ! The winner of the high jump and the gold medal is Ozzy Orca !!
That's... a lot more than 15 feet.
I can't even imagine the power it takes to do that.
How astonishing that it can launch so high with that enormous weight. Sheer power!
I never thought it was possible for orcas to jump that high. Incredible.
Awesome. He gets a Birdseye view!
What a splish splash that will be!!!
